
S -> COMMAND | QUESTION | RESPONSE

COMMAND -> V | VP | UH
QUESTION -> WHP V NP | WHP V PRO
RESPONSE -> NP V NP | PRO V NP

WHP -> WH
VP -> V P NP
V ->  'stop' | 'halt' | 'go'  | 'look' | 'point' | 'pick' | 'come' | 'is' | 'am' | 'are' | 'hate' | 'loathe'
P -> 'to' | 'at' | 'up' | 'down' | 'here'
NP -> DET SHAPE | DET ADJ SHAPE | DET ADJ ADJ SHAPE | PRO N | N | DET N
DET -> 'the' | 'a'
ADJ -> COLOR | SIZE
COLOR -> 'black' | 'blue' | 'gray' | 'green' | 'red' | 'yellow' | 'white'
SIZE -> 'small' | 'large'
SHAPE -> 'ball' | 'sphere' | 'box' | 'cube' | 'cylinder'

WH -> 'who' | 'what' | 'when' | 'where' | 'why' | 'how'
PRO -> 'your' | 'my' | 'his' | 'her' | 'i' | 'he' | 'she' | 'you'
N -> DOBJ | PROPN | STATE | MAJOR | MAJOR MAJOR
DOBJ -> 'major' | 'name' | 'weather'
STATE -> 'good' | 'well' | 'bad'
UH -> 'hello' | 'hi'
PROPN -> PERSON
PERSON -> 'jon' | 'jonathan' | 'steve' | 'bob' | 'derek' | 'diana' | 'daniel'
MAJOR -> 'computer' | 'science' | 'astronomy' | 'physics' | 'engineering' | 'philosophy' | 'psychology' | 'music'

